{
  "stem": "21310.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the upper part was some kind of a felt that I think was made out of old newspapers or something or cardboard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, and somehow, it was treated chemically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they were making boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were making all kinds of scarves out of dying-- you know, sheets that were being dyed different colors and then [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Most of the peasant women wore these babushkas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So there were these babushkas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was a, a almost a thriving economy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was being smuggled out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I assume most of them was smuggled out with the knowledge of the Germans because-- with bribery and, and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so some-- and exchange, again, for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I guess you heard about these children that were going through the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] over the, the brick wall, or rather, under the, the wall with digging holes and getting out of the ghetto and bringing in food, smuggling in food.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I was caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans could come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, there were labor battalions that were coming out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could come to-- going to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans also, when they needed some special work or something, they would come in and catch people in the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was caught once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I was caught several times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But once, the worst experience I had was when they took me to some kind of a big building, well, like barracks for soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a like big building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if it was a old school or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave me a pail of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave me some cold water and they told me to wash the windows and-- outside and inside.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
